title: Black Hat USA 2023
description: Now in its 26th year, Black Hat USA returns to the Mandalay Bay Convention Center in Las Vegas with a 6-day program. The event will open with four days of specialized cybersecurity Trainings (August 5-10), with courses for all skill levels. The two-day main conference (August 9-10) will feature more than 100 selected Briefings, dozens of open-source tool demos in Arsenal, a robust Business Hall, networking and social events, and much more. This year Black Hat is launching 'Certified Pentester' program - a full day practical exam, covering pentesting topics. See the Conference Highlights below for more details.
